<plot>A story of "people power" - the story follows three ordinary heroes - Pam, Craig, and Rudy - who use medical marijuana to alleviate the symptoms of serious medical conditions like cancer. The three of them decide to fight for their rights against local politicians who try to overturn Proposition 215. the California Law passed in 1996 that approved the use of medical marijuana.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?471456</url></doc>
